					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You can remove a few tiles at the sides (they will not be visible anyway due to overscan), this will give you a bit more of room to play with.<br /><br />Also if you can afford it, consider alternating the position of the scanlines (60FPS blinking, yeah), that will reduce the strippiness (and before somebody comments on seizures, strips also cause them anyway, if anything this may make it <em>less</em> prone to cause them due to being harder to see).</div>

